            "englishShloka": "vipanchit supanchamam ruchir venuna gayata \npriyen sahavinaya madhurgan vidyanidhih \nkarindravanasammilanmad karinyudarakrama \nkada nu vrushabhanuja milatu bhanujarodhasi",
