            "englishShloka": "saa lavanya chamatkrutirnav vayo rupam ch tanmohanam \ntatatkeli kala vilas lahari chaturyamaascharya bhuh \nno kinchitkrutamev yatra na nutirnago na va sambhramo \nradhaamadhavayoh sa ko̕pi sahajah premotsavah patu vah",
