            "englishShloka": "romalimihiratmaja sulalite bandhuk bandhu prabha \nsarvange sphut champakacchhaviraho nabhi sarah shobhana \nvakshojastabaka lasadbhujalta shinjapatanjhankrutih \nshriradha harate mano madhupateranyev vrundaatavi",
