            "englishShloka": "radhaamadhavayorvichitra suratarambhe nikunjodar \nsrast prastarasangatairvapuralam kurveng ragaih kada \ntatraiv trutitah srajo nipatitah sandhayabhuyah kada \nkanthe dharyitasmi marjan krute pratah pravishtasmyaham",
