            "englishShloka": "kotinduchabi hasini nav sudha sambhar sambhashini \nvakshoj dvitayen hem kalash shrigarva nirvasini \nchitra gram nivasini nav nav premotsavollasini \nvrundaranya vilasini kimu raho bhuyad dhrudullasini",
