            "englishShloka": "oshth prantocchhalit dayitodgirna tambul raga \nraganuchairnij rachitaya chitra bhangyonnayanti \ntiryaggrivaa ruchir ruchirodanchada kunchit bhruh \npreyah parshve vipul pulakairmandita bhati radha",
